  SYNTAX:  changelog [categories | [all|new] [category]]

Lists all changelog entries in reverse order so newest entries are
first. If neither [all] or [new] are passed as arguments, the most
recent 5 entries are shown.

Optional Arguments:
[categories] - Lists all optional categories.

[all] - Lists all entries regardless of age.
[new] - Lists only the newest entry.
        Mutually exclusive, only one or the other can be used.

