             Can be combined with [all] or [new].

This list will not be all inclusive and exhaustive, nor will it
include changes that are documented elsewhere, such as guild,
crafting, profession, or other places where files like 'info new'
already exist for tracking such changes.

Whether something is added to this list is up to the discretion
of the wizard management.
