anywhere until you choose to save it to the autotyper or a local file
within the Portal.

 PLEASE NOTE: YOU MUST HAVE CLIENT VERSION 2.0 OR GREATER TO USE THIS COMMAND.

All downloaded files may be accessed through the little blue jewel on
your main output screen.  It's in the upper left corner.

If you wish to provide delay or chunk size you must also provide
all the preceding arguments as well.

Delay is a number of CPU cycles to wait between each line.  A high
value in this will crap out cled from Too many Eval cycles.  This
argument is only useful if you have a really bad connection or other
such issues.

