aliases: 
short: Item Briefer
header: Topic: Item Brief

  SYNTAX:  ibrief [<arg> | all [on|off] | needed <arg> | [on|off] <arg>]

     Item Briefing
 Commands:
  ibrief              - Lists briefed items in your inventory.
  ibrief <arg>        - Toggles brief on <arg> in your inventory.
  ibrief on <arg>     - Toggles brief on for <arg> in your inventory.
  ibrief off <arg>    - Toggles brief off for <arg> in your inventory.
  ibrief all [on|off] - Toggles brief on/off for your entire inventory.
  ibrief needed <arg> - Logs an item that should allow briefing.

 ibrief will, on an item by item basis, block some/all messages 
 from the item to reduce your combat spam. Each item must be
 individually coded for this to work. If you find an item that does
 not support briefing but should, use 'ibrief needed <arg>' to tag
 the item for wizards to add the functionality to it.

 Note: Ibrief affects what *you* see and will not generally affect
       what is displayed to the room/others.

 Also note, dropping an item will reset its brief setting.

