    reflex <remove | delete> <hp/sp/gp1/gp2> <number|%> -Deletes a reflex.
    reflex <start | unpause | enable>      -Starts all reflexes.
    reflex <stop | pause | disable>        -Stops all reflexes.
    reflex <clear | reset>                 -Removes all reflexes.
    reflex clear <hp|sp|gp1|gp2>           -Removes corresponding reflexes.
