short: Stop hunting your previous target
header: Topic: Stop

  Syntax: stop

If you have wimpied or left the room while fighting a monster,
it will be hunting you, and will attack you on sight the next
time you encounter it.  Similarly, if a monster or player you
were fighting leaves the room that you are in, you will be
hunting it, and will automatically attack it the next time you
