to hide themselves from visibility on the who list.  Linkdead players are
visible on the list until 2 hours or more linkdead, at which point they are
considered 'Ethereal' and are not listed individually.  Linkdead players
(ethereal or not) are still able to receive tells, in which case they will
be notified upon their return.

