aliases: 
short: In a bugged dark room with no exits?  No problem!
header: Topic: Bugfree

  SYNTAX:  bugfree

If you ever find yourself stuck in a dark room with no exits,
it is most likely bugged.  Not all no-exit rooms are bugged, but
you will probably know it if you see it.  Before you go calling
for a wizard to help you, please try the 'bugfree' command.  If
indeed the room is bugged, you will be transported to the login
room and a report will be written for the wizards to address.

If you are not transported, the room isn't bugged, and you have
to find another way to exit the room.


