file: /help/CMDS/omp
keywords: mortal, mortal, chatlines, communication
aliases:
short: OMP - The OFFICIAL 3-Kingdoms Mud Party
header: OMP - The OFFICIAL 3-Kingdoms Mud Party
syntax: omp <message>

The 'omp' command allows you to speak on the OMP party line.  This 
line follows standard mud chatline rules and toggle options.

  >>> NOTE: This line is to be used for OMP Discussion ONLY <<<

What is the OMP?
Every year, The Marble Group organizes an 'Official Mud Party'
that is open to all denizens of 3Kingdoms and their families.
These annual OMPs are held in major cities around the continental
United States at a specific venue, typically a large hotel.  The
OMP is a multi-day event, with various activities that occur from
Thursday through Saturday.  Technically, Saturday evening/night is
the actual OMP event, which includes organized food, prizes and all
sorts of cool stuff.  Even though things aren't normally scheduled
for Wendesday, people tend to show up that day, or even earlier!

Why go to an OMP?
An OMP gives players from all over the world the chance to come
together and meet others who play 3Kingdoms.  It is a chance to
sit down and talk to people you might never have met otherwise,
and also a chance to meet friends you see year after year.  The
weekend is always packed with gatherings, movies, games, parties
and site-specific activities for all.

Is this an adults-only gathering?
In general, the OMP can be considered an 'adult' event, but that
doesn't mean that spouses and families aren't welcome or enjoyed.
Just be aware that there may be some adult language at times.
Seeing as one of the owners brings his own family every year,
you can be assured that offensive behavior of any kind is not
tolerated and violators are asked to leave.

Did you say prizes?
Yes!!  Every year The Marble Group provides a HUGE list of prizes
to be won.  Some are given to event champions, but the bulk will
go to the door-prize raffle, in which everyone has a chance to go
home with some VERY cool gear.  Past prizes have included computer
systems, video game systems of all kinds, digital cameras, MP3
players, GPS units, swords, 3Kingdoms gear and hundreds of other
goodies.

When is the next OMP?
