keywords: spawn, second, character, seconds, multiple, characters
aliases: 
short: Spawnsecond
header: Topic: Second Characters

  SYNTAX: spawnsecond <charactername>

Legally spawns an additional character, linking it to your other character(s).
All your current characters must be at least level 50 to do this.

        * * * * * READ THE INSTRUCTIONS CAREFULLY * * * * *

1) Create (and login) your new character (example: Bob)
2) Once 'Bob' is logged in, login an existing character of yours
3) With both logged in, on your existing character, type 'spawnsecond bob'
