short: Take off armour
header: Remove - take off armour

 SYNTAX:  remove <armour> | all

Use the remove command to take off your worn armour.  Note that if an item
is cursed, you will have to uncurse it in order to remove it.  Also, you
cannot remove rings if you are wearing gauntlets or gloves.

'remove all' will remove all of your worn equipment.


