The 'wield' command will allow you to wield a weapon.  Be aware that 
you may not wield a two-handed weapon while wearing a shield.

Many weapons have special powers that may be determined through 
experimentation with the weapon.

Several guilds have restrictions on the types of weapons 
that may be wielded--be sure to ask a member of a particular guild
for weapon restrictions particular to that guild.


