file: /help/MISC/binding
keywords: bind, equipment, boe, bop
aliases: binding
short: Binding Equipment
header: Binding Equipment

3K has a special class of items and equipment in the realms called binding
equipment.  There are two types of binding : Bind on Equip (BOE) and Bind on
Pickup (BOP).  Items that bind on equip do not bind until they are worn or 
wielded.  Items that bind on pickup are bound the moment they are taken off 
the ground.  Oftentimes there is no warning before an item binds to you, so 
pay attention, but most items will state their binding type in its description
when examined.  

Once an item is bound to you, it is bound for an entire reboot and will be
unusable by others.  All bound items can be taken to the gypsy when they are 
no longer of use - Mr. Mistoffoles offers a substantial reward.


