file: /help/autoload
keywords: general,autoload
aliases: autoload boot
short: Special reward boot: Autoloading Gear
header: Reward for OMP VAF season, the Autoload Boot

Usually once yearly, there's an "autoload boot" where all of the
equipment you've gathered will carry into the next boot.  This is
generally reserved as a special reward for the OMP VAF drive.

The basics are: Gear you have on you will survive if you quit
and log back in.
However, those basics have several exceptions:
1) No corpses or bioplasts
2) Contents of bags will be lost (so 'get all from bag')
3) You must actually be carrying it when you quit
4) Special items...

There are some items in the game that are special.  The most notable
ones being "crafted" gear.  These items have no memory from one boot
to the next and thus will not come back the same (if at all.)
Another example are drinks from the Pinnacle Palisade Pub.

Lastly, gear that spawns with random special abilities or at
random power levels will have that same level of randomness when
it returns the next boot.

All of this is, unfortunately, unavoidable.

And, of course, most gear will load just fine.

