file: /help/legal
keywords: legal, corporation
aliases: corporation, marble, the marble group
short: Legal Status of The Marble Group
header: Legal Status of The Marble Group

The Marble Group is a legal incorporated entity within the state
of Michigan, USA.  The business that The Marble Group partakes
in, namely the running of an online game, does not qualify for
non-profit status, and as such, The Marble Group is a "for profit"
organization complete with shareholders.  The term "for profit" is
a bit of a misnomer, however, since no one gets paid a salary and
all of TMG's income goes directly into an account to pay ISP fees,
OMP fees, advertising, and all marble/server/game related expenses.

It is important to note that The Marble Group owns the marble
machine (the machine the game runs on) and all software that dwells
upon the marble machine, including but not limited to the mud
driver code, area code, and all aspects of 3Kingdoms and 3Scapes.

You can read 'help vaf' on how you can aid the game's operating fund.

(These monetary contributions are not referred to as donations for
 legal reasons as well.  Since we are not (and can not be) a
 non-profit corporation we cannot refer to them as donations.)


