keywords: general, communication, tell, addlink, dislink, checklink, ignorelink, talk, talke, mywhosync
aliases: linktells
short: How to use linktells.
header: Linktell: How to talk to several people at once.
Linktells and how to use them:

By using a 'linktell', you are able to communicate with several
people at once.

     addlink - add a person to your linktell.
     dislink - remove a person from your linktell.
     checklink - check which people are on your linktell.
     ignorelink - ignore all linktells.
     talk - allow you to talk on your linktell.
     talke - allow you to emote on your linktell.
     mywhosync - set your linktell with people from your mywho list

Each of the above commands has its own help file for more information.

You are limited to 6 people on a linktell at once.
Type 'help vaf' to learn how to double this maximum.


