The Player Advisory Board

The Player Advisory Board, or PAB, as it will be referred to from now
on, is a group of players selected by the Playerbase as a whole, and
the 3k Administration.

The purpose of the PAB is for Titled Wizards(Solar+) to have a 
sounding board to bounce ideas off of, and to get input on upcoming 
changes to make the game better, bring things back in balance, or 
anything else they feel the need to consult on.

Please note, that this is an ADVISORY Board, not a policy-making Board.

Membership, at least in the beginning, will be as follows:
-Titled Wizards
-Two(2) Players chosen by the Playerbase.
-One(1) Player chosen by the Solars.
-One(1) Player chosen by the Archons.
This can be adjusted as needed, depending on the scope of the current
discussion, and if Administration feels the need.

