file: /help/pk
keywords: general, kill, arena, clanworld, anarchy, invasion, bloodmatch
aliases: pking, PK
short:  Player Killing On 3K
header: Player Killing

PK is PK.  Read the PK board for more information or ask some other
mud folks.

Furthermore, a log exists that records when PKers LD or quit out of
battle. The punishment for doing this will be 1 off of your primary
stat and 1 off of a secondary stat of random choice.  Why? Because
quitting out of battle ruins the essence of PK.

Interfering non-PKers, beware...
If a person of Non PK status chooses to participate in the demise or triumph
of a PK player, that person is in essence claiming their desire to be PK.
This desire will be granted.  Let's spell this out in very clear terms:
If you are not PK and you help a PKer to live or die in a battle, you will
be patched PK yourself.  This means healing, giving potions, tracking
locations, or aiding in some other way.  We don't care what your guild
policy is, so read this a few times if it wasn't clear.

Oh, and mentioning PK to any admin, or bitching about it, or discussing
it anywhere beyond the confines of PK sanctioned areas is grounds for death.

Type 'help vaf' to learn how to remove your playerkiller status.


